189/* Authentication Type Flags */
190#define WPS_AUTH_OPEN 0x0001
191#define WPS_AUTH_WPAPSK 0x0002
192#define WPS_AUTH_SHARED 0x0004 /* deprecated */
193#define WPS_AUTH_WPA 0x0008
194#define WPS_AUTH_WPA2 0x0010
195#define WPS_AUTH_WPA2PSK 0x0020
196#define WPS_AUTH_TYPES (WPS_AUTH_OPEN | WPS_AUTH_WPAPSK | WPS_AUTH_SHARED | \
197 WPS_AUTH_WPA | WPS_AUTH_WPA2 | WPS_AUTH_WPA2PSK)
198
199/* Encryption Type Flags */
200#define WPS_ENCR_NONE 0x0001
201#define WPS_ENCR_WEP 0x0002 /* deprecated */
202#define WPS_ENCR_TKIP 0x0004
203#define WPS_ENCR_AES 0x0008
204#define WPS_ENCR_TYPES (WPS_ENCR_NONE | WPS_ENCR_WEP | WPS_ENCR_TKIP | \
205 WPS_ENCR_AES)
